title: #230: Unconservative and Incorrect (@NickDipaolo)
itunes:title: Unconservative and Incorrect with Nick DiPaolo
description: Nick Dipaolo met me at my apartment to talk about how he's not a conservative and how Libertarians feel about conservativism and political correctness. Fun podcast and I finished it only minutes before I leave for Scotland for all of August. So long, America.
